"My
first
enjoyment,"
replied
John
Knightley,
as
they
passed
through
the
sweep
gate,
"will
be
to
find
myself
safe
at
Hartfield
again."
Some
change
of
countenance
was
necessary
for
each
gentleman
as
they
walked
into
Mrs.
Weston's
drawing
room;
Mr.
Elton
must
compose
his
joyous
